re slippage.  This condition can vary by terrain type.</comment><data>{"commentRefs":[],"fieldData":{"~commentOffsetX":"16","~commentOffsetY":"16"}}</data><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="ojWV%dFUNtz|dv40$Sbs"><field name="NUM">20</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="qLxkzlF%kgdWmn?*,MM$"><field name="VAR" id="Pn4_q~v_/TkrLShW@pU.">accel_rate</field><comment pinned="false" h="109" w="459">This variable controls the rate of the acceleration ramp-- how long the bot takes to get from zero to max. In initial testing 1 worked well, 2 produced tire slippage.</comment><data>{"commentRefs":[],"fieldData":{"~commentOffsetX":"16","~commentOffsetY":"16"}}</data><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id=":WD/Rz-kMNRsKo]v{6rQ"><field name="NUM">1</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="!|_fQJDAu3Ts%-1NfvFq"><field name="VAR" id="`=ApUrD}(0qDd^Yp4(rh">max_normal_speed</field><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="+a(bYw`_Y.6xgXet.u;0"><field name="NUM">60</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="~0n$Ia;M+tUJ4t|p|ST3"><field name="VAR" id="Bdy2d{-@DtkKH1)=c_,-">max_turbo_speed</field><comment pinned="false" h="119" w="369">This value will determine the maximum speed to which the bot will accelerate before topping out. Valid range is 0 to 100.</comment><data>{"commentRefs":[],"fieldData":{"~commentOffsetX":"16","~commentOffsetY":"16"}}</data><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="F$wV|[UIP`usw5!,4-p["><field name="NUM">99</field></shadow></value><next><block type="quest_Note_1_quest_Show_String_For_Note_Big_Func" id="{:vAL)R:WZU,hN%:+hWD"><value name="textStrIn"><shadow type="text" id="`x`nhBlwT%,kk^xWk/^C"><field name="TEXT">Below, Setup Code for Student:</field></shadow></value></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></statement></bl